{
  "title": "What is D&M's Security Framework?",
  "slug": "what-is-the-dm-custom-security-framework",
  "categorySlug": "security-compliance",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">What is D&amp;M's Security Framework?</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Security is D&amp;M's absolute top priority - now we can´t tell you all but here are some highlights.\n</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><div class=\"hs-callout-type-note\" data-hs-callout-type=\"note\">\n<ol>\n<li>All communication between servers and browsers is encrypted</li>\n<li>We use app registration for office365</li>\n<li>We use SSL, TLS 1.3</li>\n<li>Our VPN is based on OpenVPN due to its transparency and quality</li>\n<li>All data is encrypted in transit and at rest</li>\n<li>We continually monitor for abnormalities</li>\n<li>We scan for known vulnerabilities in both custom code and commercial applications.</li>\n<li>We are ISAE 3000 and 3402 certified.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p><img alt=\"image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"322\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=322&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=344&amp;height=161&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=322&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=1032&amp;height=483&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=1376&amp;height=644&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=1720&amp;height=805&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png?width=2064&amp;height=966&amp;name=image-png-Mar-14-2024-10-18-01-7164-AM.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">- dataflow for Microsoft - flow model for other data sources available upon request to: support@dataandmore.com<br><br>Please note:<br>1. The Data Responsible keeps control of <strong>access</strong> to the&nbsp; Microsoft 365 data</p>\n<p>2. The Data Responsible keeps control of the <strong>scope</strong> of the Microsoft 365 data</p>\n<p>3. Transport of data between the Compliance Server and Microsoft 365 is encrypted using TLS 1.3</p>\n<p>4. The Data Responsible can at any time revoke access, and all data will be deleted in the Compliance Server within 72 hours<br><br><strong>Standard Security Framework (SSF)</strong></p>\n<p>D&amp;M have developed a high-security framework for monitoring, accessing, updating and maintaining the DMCSs. An abstract of the framework can be made available to enterprise customers on a need-to-know basis and presupposes an NDA. Part of the framework consists of layered VPN connections with point-to-point access as well as a number of other monitoring and encryption services. The technology used for VPN is OpenVPN, which provides transparency in implementation and highly stable encryption. The organizational aspect of the D&amp;M SF is covered in the ISAE 3000 and ISAE 3042</p>\n<br>\n<p><strong>Custom Security Framework (CSF)</strong></p>\n<p>For some enterprise customers, the D&amp;M Standard security framework is not compatible with the enterprise policies. In such cases, D&amp;M can accept the Custom Security Framework - as long as it does not compromise any of D&amp;M's security policies. Any access to the DMCS other than D&amp;M Point-to-Point OpenVPN connections will require a CSF clearance by D&amp;M Security. This includes access to customer data via services such as&nbsp; RDB, Citrix, and GlobalConnect. Any customer that requires a CSF must obtain both a Premium and a CSF subscription on the DMCS.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"ISAE 3402 Black\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" style=\"width: 132px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=132&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png\" width=\"132\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=66&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 66w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=132&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 132w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=198&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 198w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=264&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 264w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=330&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 330w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203402%20Black.png?width=396&amp;name=ISAE%203402%20Black.png 396w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 132px) 100vw, 132px\"> <img alt=\"ISAE 3000 Black\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" style=\"width: 132px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=132&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png\" width=\"132\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=66&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 66w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=132&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 132w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=198&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 198w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=264&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 264w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=330&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 330w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISAE%203000%20Black.png?width=396&amp;name=ISAE%203000%20Black.png 396w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 132px) 100vw, 132px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
